# Top 12 Automated Ticketing Systems to Improve Support in 2025
## Introduction
Your customer support is the lifeline of your business. A good product might not be enough if your support falls short, leading to deferred opportunities, dwindling trust, and damaged reputation. Manual ticketing processes can quickly become unsustainable, overwhelming your team and damaging customer satisfaction.

## What is an Automated Ticketing System?
An automated ticketing system streamlines and accelerates customer support by automatically assigning, routing, and prioritizing incoming tickets. It empowers teams to provide faster, consistent resolutions and makes customer experience seamless through automation and smart workflows.

